column5: just thought i'd toss together a slideshow of some of the fish i've landed so far this season, i havn't got out quite as much as i'd like to and most is local but i still have had a great time, and we all know everyone loves a few pictures.
Looks like you really had a great season.Nice multi species show.Thanks for that  Tite Lines Paul
wtg Miller ... looks like you are having a lot of fun this year.
yeah i've had a pretty fun year, some quite tasty outings as well
Looks like everything is in order!  I love the food
Looks like you had a very productive summer. That Brown looks like the fish of the year for you. Thanks for sharing.
Right on, nice mixed bag of fish..... 	way to diversify!
yeah it definatly was, gorgeous fish and great fights, i lost a few other scrappy ones this past spring as well.
